      "content": "i know i should talk to them but it just feels so selfish to keep adding more to their plate. every time they come over, they're just more exhausted because of me. sometimes i think i'd be doing them a favor if i just weren't around to make things so difficult. it seems like the only way i can actually help them is to stop being a problem.",
